Reimer, A. and Reimer, O. and Ritz, S. and Roth, M. and Sadrozinski, H. F.W. and Sbarra, C. and Scargle, J. D. and Schalk, T. L. and Sgr{\`{o}}, C. and Siskind, E. J. and Spandre, G. and Spinelli, P. and Strigari, L. and Suson, D. J. and Tajima, H. and Takahashi, H. and Tanaka, T. and Thayer, J. G. and Thayer, J. B. and Thompson, D. J. and Tibaldo, L. and Tinivella, M. and Torres, D. F. and Troja, E. and Uchiyama, Y. and Vandenbroucke, J. and Vasileiou, V. and Vianello, G. and Vitale, V. and Waite, A. P. and Wang, P. and Winer, B. L. and Wood, K. S. and Wood, M. and Yang, Z. and Zimmer, S. and Kaplinghat, M. and Martinez, G. D.},
doi = {10.1103/PhysRevLett.107.241302},
